===Etymology===
{{liushu|p}}; originally a stylized picture of clouds. The character was subsequently borrowed for a homophonous word meaning "say" and the original meaning came to be represented by [[雲]], through the addition of the [[雨]] ("rain") component. The simplified form eliminates this later addition and uses 云 for both "say" and "cloud".

